Package valworkbench.measures.internal.FOM

Class Summary
FigureOfMerit The FigureOfMerit is the base class for all FOM measures.
FOMFast The FOMFast class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Fast Figure Of Merit.
FOMFastA The FOMFastA class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Fast Figure Of Merit and relative assessment by computing average adjusted rand index.
FOMGeneric The FOMGeneric class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit.
FOMGenericA The FOMGenericA class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit with Assessment.
FOMHierarchical The FOMHierarchical class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit for Hierarhical algorithms.
FOMHierarchicalA The FOMHierarchicalA class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit for Hierarhical algorithms and relative assessment obtained through computing of average adjusted rand values.
FOMHierarchicalInit The FOM_Generic_Hierarchical_Init class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit with Hierarchical Initialization.
FOMHierarchicalInitA The FOMGenericHierarchicalInitA class provides an Object that encapsulates methods and all the informations for computing Figure Of Merit and relative assessment for Hierarchical Initialization.
